type="postscript" mimetype="application" xlink:href="elife-26902-fig1-v1"/></fig></p><p>The originally published Figure 1 is also shown for reference:<fig id="fig2" position="float"><graphic mime-subtype="x-tiff" mimetype="image" xlink:href="elife-26902-fig2-v1"/></fig></p><p>The article has been corrected accordingly.</p></body></article>